PKNA #1

Ombre su Venere / Shadows on Venus

The journalist Angus Fangus is attacked by an Evronian patrol; Pk foils the kidnapping thanks to the vengeful alien Xadhoom; nevertheless, Fangus is hit by a semi-coolflamizzato evrongun.

Thanks to the interstellar ship placed on top of Ducklair Tower, the protagonists go to Evronian headquarters in geostationary orbit around Venus.
